        lomb (>= 1.0)
Imports: boot, broom, doParallel, foreach, iterators, parallel,
        plotrix, PMCMRplus, segmented, stats, tibble, tidyr, writexl
Suggests: tcltk, tkrplot, knitr, rmarkdown
